data.description: Walk in with equity! Welcome to this stunning two-story home that perfectly balances modern design and comfortable living. This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem boasts a new roof and an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly blends spaciousness and functionality. As you enter the main level, you're greeted by an airy living area that flows effortlessly into the dining space and kitchen where you will find a secondary living or formal dining area entertained by a mantled fireplace.  The oversized kitchen is a chef's dream offering beautiful granite countertops, ample cabinetry for storage, and a center island that serves as both a preparation area and a breakfast bar, making it the heart of the home where family and friends can gather. Adjacent to the kitchen is a convenient half bathroom for guests & a bonus room that can double as a study or hobby room. Upstairs, you'll find the master suite, complete with a walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bathroom. The master bathroom boasts dual sinks, a spacious shower, and tasteful finishes.  The upper level shares two additional well-appointed bedrooms, and another full bathroom with a tub providing comfortable accommodations for family members or guests. One of the standout features of this home is the versatile loft area that can be transformed into a home office, a playroom, or a cozy reading nook, depending on your needs!  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite open floor plan home your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort, style, and convenience it has to offer!
